{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji24.pdf"],"article":{"title":"致中原局电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致中原局电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年7月13日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粟兵团应在现地区作战至明年春季或夏季，歼灭五军、十八军等部，开辟南进道路，然后南进（不歼灭五军、十八军不走)。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的致中原局并告粟裕、陈士、唐亮电的主要内容。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1948,"month":7,"day":13}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":342,"page_end":342},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}